formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
"The Promoter has entered in to Development Agreement with land owners on Bartering model, in which the Promoter shall construct a unit admeasuring 1312.56 Sq. mtr. Carpet area for the land owners against conveying development rights by land owners in favour of Promoter.There shall not be any actual payment of land cost as there is barter system in the case. The land cost for the project is taken only to derive the project cost. The land cost for the project is taken as certified by the management . The area offered to land owner i.e 1312.56 is not offered for sale hence it is not forming part of the CA Certificate. We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost. The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances.The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA , Carpet Area, No of parking, unit consideration etc is taken as certified by the management. KYC details of the customer is taken as provided by the promoter."As informed to us by the management there is no material lying unused on the date of certification. We have not scrutinised the books of accounts we have taken the data as provided by the management. in the earlier certification the number of booked inventory is changed in this certification as earlier the unit numbers were incorrectly provided by the promoter which is corrected in this return.
